items.text:
**CASTINGOPSLAG – KORTFILM “ALT I INTET”**

Vi søger **skuespillere i alderen 18–23 år** til hovedrollerne i vores kommende **ulønnede kortfilm** *Alt I Intet*.
**Forplejning vil være inkluderet under optagelserne.**
Projektet har ambitioner om festivaldeltagelse og ønsker at skabe et værk, der kan nå ud til et bredere publikum.

**Om projektet**

*”Alt I Intet”* er et karakterdrevet drama, der undersøger temaer som kærlighed, sorg og identitet. Filmen bevæger sig i grænselandet mellem virkelighed og erindring og skildrer en ung mands indre rejse efter et stort tab.

**Om os**

Vi er tre unge filmskabere med en fælles passion for at skabe stærke fortællinger og ambitiøse filmiske værker med fokus på stemning, følelser og karakterudvikling.

 

**Roller**

**Oliver (mand, 18–23 år)**
Oliver er en ung, følsom og reflekterende mand, der er dybt knyttet til sine relationer. Udadtil fremstår han stille og næsten anonym, som om han bevæger sig gennem hverdagen på autopilot. Han lever primært i minderne om sin afdøde kæreste, som fortsat påvirker hans hverdag og selvforståelse.

**Emma (kvinde, 18–23 år)**
Emma er en varm, nærværende og livlig ung kvinde, der formår at se Oliver, når han ikke selv kan. Hun repræsenterer både kærlighed, tryghed og det liv, Oliver har mistet.

 

**Logline**

Fortabt i minderne om Emma genoplever Oliver sit tab på grænsen mellem virkelighed og hallucinationer, indtil et møde mellem liv og død giver ham et nyt blik på sig selv – og på det liv, der stadig venter.

 

**Optagedatoer**

**Lørdag d. 7. marts – søndag d. 8. marts**

**Lørdag d. 14. marts – søndag d. 15. marts**

 

**Vigtig information**

Da filmen behandler temaer som kærlighed og sorg, vil der indgå semi-intime scener, herunder kram, håndholdning og tæt fysisk kontakt.

For den kvindelige rolle forekommer der enkelte scener i badetøj. Disse scener har ingen seksuel karakter og vil blive behandlet med respekt og tydelig kommunikation.

 

**Ansøgning**

Vi ser gerne, at interesserede sender følgende:

**Selftape**

**Portrætbillede**

**Alder og højde**

Ansøgning og eventuelle spørgsmål kan sendes via:
**E-mail:** magn715c@gmail.com
**Messenger: **Undertegnet

Vi ser frem til at høre fra jer.

 

**Venlig hilsen**
**Magnus Petersen**
Producer – ”*Alt I Intet”*
på vegne af filmens crew

sharedPost.text:
Happy Holidays from Selfcast 🎄✨
To all our talents, producers, casters and partners — thank you for an unforgettable 2025. We’re sharing this beautiful new film with Søstrene Grene as a little holiday gift and a huge thank you for the trust, teamwork and artistry this year. 💫

We just lived the dream. ✨
So proud that Selfcast helped bring Søstrene Grene’s first international brand campaign to life — with a powerful cast of ballet dancers who gave the film its heartbeat.

As Choreographer/Caster — Maria Christina Jarltoft, it felt like the best kind of time warp: the craft of commercials from 25 years ago — and a heartbeat back on stage from my ballet years.

Full credits & thanks to:
Agency/Creative: @boyespellerberg @Pobeyboye
Directors: @storm__hansen @michaelhansen_mic @tuewstorm
Production: @nicolai_berthelsen
Casting/Choreography: @Selfcastapp — @mariachristinaselfcast
Stylist: @hlindvig

Our incredible ballet cast: @emmajarltoft @valdemarwalter @sara.diona @nahiagilharris @josephine2605 @ameliaidabang

Post/VFX: @hitchvfx @chemistry_film @larsenvfx
Rasmus Skjøtt, René Tingskov, Lotte Korntved, Jacob Holst Mouritzen, Dennis Lee
… and a long list of dedicated people across 17+ markets.

Thank you all — and Merry Christmas & Happy New Year!
Please tag anyone I missed below so we can add everyone who made this happen. 🙏

#Selfcast #CastingMadeEasy #Ballet #Choreography #InternationalCampaign #SøstreneGrene #Production #Creativity #BrandFilm #HappyHolidays #MerryChristmas

items.text:
Chcesz być animatorem, którego pamiętają, polecają i zapraszają ponownie?
Nie wystarczy „zabawić grupę”.
Dziś animator to lider emocji, energii i atmosfery wydarzenia 💥

Dlatego stworzyliśmy szkolenie Animacja Czasu Wolnego,
czyli najbardziej praktyczne szkolenie dla animatorów w Polsce!

📍 Poznań | 24.01.2026

To nie jest kolejne szkolenie z teorii.
To intensywny dzień pełen praktyki, narzędzi i inspiracji, które możesz wdrożyć od razu do swojej pracy! 

Dlaczego warto?
✨️Wyróżnisz się na rynku animatorów
✨️Zwiększysz swoją wartość i atrakcyjność dla klientów i pracodawców
✨️Zyskasz pewność siebie w prowadzeniu grupy
✨️Wyjdziesz z głową pełną pomysłów i sercem pełnym energii 

To szkolenie to inwestycja w Twoją markę, rozwój i przyszłe zlecenia!

👉 Zapisz się teraz:
🌐 www.STAGEMAN.pl

Liczba miejsc jest ograniczona - pracujemy w kameralnych grupach, żeby każdy dostał realną wartość.

Jeśli chcesz być animatorem, który robi różnicę, a nie tylko „robi hałas” - widzimy się w Poznaniu! 😃

items.text:
**Szukam modelki na zasadzie TFP Gliwice/Katowice ( Śląsk ) 03.01.26 godz. 15.00 – 17.00**

 

Szukam pań które nie krępują się własnego ciała i chciałaby mieć ciekawą pamiątkę w postaci klimatycznych zdjęć sensualnych. Wiem jak bardzo jest ważna akceptacja własnego ciała bo przez to też możemy inaczej funkcjonować. Przez takie zdjęcia można również tego dokonać. Sesja w głównej mierze jest jako taki motywator.

 

Poszukuje kobiety w **wieku od 35 **lat nie koniecznie z doświadczeniem pozowania, na zasadach **TFP**  mieszkającej w Gliwicach lub okolicach Zabrze czy Katowice najdalej. Posiadam na wyposażeniu mini studio z kilkoma tłami oraz lampami. Mam również duży wybór kostiumów i gadżetów do wykorzystywania. Główny motyw do kobieta: Piękna i drapieżna! Sama sesja trwa przeważnie od 1,5h do 2h w zalezności od motywów.

** **

** **

**Zapraszam na stronę**

** **

**Facebook Łukasz Magiera – Fotografia**

www.instagram.com/lukasz.magiera.official

Więcej informacji na Priv

items.text:
With 2026 right around the corner The Audition Pal are thrilled to be announcing our first 2026 workshop- and it’s a big one 

Sophie Pearson Casting will be hosting a Zoom workshop on the morning of 17th January (GMT). 

Here’s a Bio on Sophie Below:

Sophie started her career working as an associate for Ros and John Hubbard, where she worked on projects such as “Journey’s End” (Directed by Saul Dibb), ‘The More You Ignore Me’ (Directed by Keith English), and ‘Time of Our Lives’ (Directed by Roger Goldby). She then worked at Des Hamilton Casting, where she cast noteworthy ventures like “Hilma” (Directed by Lasse Hallström), the Netflix sensation “Top Boy,” “The King” (Directed by David Michôd), “Jojo Rabbit” (Directed by Taika Watiti), and “My First Film” (Directed by Zia Anger). Since starting Sophie Pearson Casting, Sophie has worked on many projects including ‘Vows’ starring Sarah Parish and Eddie Marsan and ‘The Man With The Urn’ starring Ciaran Hinds, Olga Kurlenko and Stephen Fry. Sophie is also working alongside Dan Hubbard Casting, on projects such as the TV series ‘The Gentleman’ (directed by Guy Ritchie) and ‘The Rage’ (directed by Paul Greengrass).

We are so excited for this one! So DM us on the platform or email us at: theauditionpals@gmail.com 

Here are the links to our free platform for Actors. Never pay or struggle for a read in for your auditions again! Join us if not on the platform already! 

https://www.facebook.com/share/g/1DXYi988sL/?mibextid=wwXIfr

https://www.instagram.com/theauditionpal?igsh=aGNoYm92dnJxZmM4&utm_source=qr

items.text:
30 min Short Film / Proof-of-concept pilot Episode (Graduation Project)

We are casting PAZUZU, a supernatural entity in a dark, poetic fantasy-horror pilot.

Age: Open (25s–40s)

Gender: Open

Location: Berlin

Production: Independent / Graduation Project

Compensation: Unpaid, meals + credits + content for showreel.

Shooting days: January 19 - 24 

Pazuzu will require 2 shooting days. 

Pazuzu is not a traditional demon.

He is intelligent, unstable, and addicted to souls, not out of cruelty, but desperation. He is caught

between cosmic power and emotional decay.

This role requires:

● Strong presence and restraint

● Comfort with psychological intensity

● Ability to shift between charm, menace, humor, and vulnerability

● Voice and stillness are as important as physicality

If interested:

Please email for self-tape instructions to

celia.t@catalyst-students.com

items.text:
Marketing Macabre - a horror public relations company created to give independent filmmakers an affordable alternative. We focus on the importance of publicity to gain momentum and we work with some of the biggest genre websites in the world. Our mission is to get your project in front of your audience, the horror public - the most devoted fan base in all of entertainment.   

Our enhanced filmmaker services will supply you with everything needed on your cinematic journey from pre-production to post-production to distribution.  We have forged relationships out of trust and loyalty with partners that stretch from Hollywood studios to distribution companies.   In the evolution of horror, we have evolved from a marketing company to something more.  

A creation born out of necessity and a genesis into a one-stop-horror-shop that offers not only marketing, but opportunities in brand development, film funding, and distribution.  There are many complexities of making a feature film but our marketing militia will guide you on your journey and be your source to access the horror multiverse that is Marketing Macabre.

items.summary:
Marketing Macabre - a horror public relations company created to give independent filmmakers an affordable alternative. We focus on the importance of publicity to gain momentum and we work with some of the biggest genre websites in the world. Our mission is to get your project in front of your audience, the horror public - the most devoted fan base in all of entertainment.   

Our enhanced filmmaker services will supply you with everything needed on your cinematic journey from pre-production to post-production to distribution.  We have forged relationships out of trust and loyalty with partners that stretch from Hollywood studios to distribution companies.   In the evolution of horror, we have evolved from a marketing company to something more.  

A creation born out of necessity and a genesis into a one-stop-horror-shop that offers not only marketing, but opportunities in brand development, film funding, and distribution.  There are many complexities of making a feature film but our marketing militia will guide you on your journey and be your source to access the horror multiverse that is Marketing Macabre.

Sziasztok 🎄

Az idei év utolsó felhívása ✨

**A nagy sikerre való tekintettel idén utoljára tartunk toborzást a Januártól induló alkalmi hostess és statiszta munkáinkra. **🎉

A betöltésre váró pozíciók: 
* Rendezvényeken 💃
(vendég fogadás, márka képviselet, köszönő ajándékcsomagok összeállítása és osztása, karszalagozás)
* **Promóciókon **🎈
(termék kóstoltatás, nyereményjátékok lebonyolítása, stand képviselet, repi termékek osztása) 
* **Kérdőívezés **🤩
(elégedettségi felméréseken kérdőív kitöltetése)
* **Szórólapozás **📃
* **Háttér statisztálás **🎬
(közönség statiszta munkák a legnépszerűbb hazai Tv műsorokban, háttér statiszta munkák népszerű márkák reklámjaiban, filmekben és sorozatokban) 
* **Kiemelt statisztálás **🎤
(kiemelt statiszta munka reklámokban, filmekben, sorozatokban) 

Bérek: 5.000-60.000/nap, 1900.-3000/ óra 💸

A munkaidők átlagosan 8-10 órát vesznek igénybe.

Hétköznap, hétvégén egyaránt lehet munkával számolni. 

Ha Januártól szívesen vállalnál rendszeresen plusz munkát iskola vagy főállás mellett dobj egy üzenetet 📩

items.title: (no title)

items.text:
Do Agencji marketingowej Studio Next szukamy doświadczonego montażysty krótkich form wideo, który będzie odpowiedzialny za tworzenie materiałów dopasowanych do formatów:
* YouTube Shorts
* Instagram Reels
* Meta Reels
* TikTok

Osoby zainteresowane proszę o wysłanie CV lub Portfolio do mnie bezpośrednio lub w komentarzu.

Celem współpracy jest produkcja wysokiej jakości, angażujących i viralowych rolek, wykorzystywanych zarówno w mediach społecznościowych, jak i w kampaniach reklamowych promujących nasze inicjatywy.

Dostarczamy:

• surowy materiał wideo

• wytyczne brandowe

Oczekujemy:

• w pełni zmontowanych materiałów

• dopasowanych do trendów short-form (dźwięki, tempo, efekty)

• gotowych do użycia w social mediach i reklamach

Estetyka montażu musi być spójna z marką i reprezentować dojrzały, profesjonalny wizerunek, skierowany do przedsiębiorców 40+.

Szukamy wyczucia, smaku i świadomego, dojrzałego podejścia do short-form contentu.

Wymagania:
* minimum kilkuletnie doświadczenie w montażu krótkich form wideo
* dziesiątki zrealizowanych materiałów w podobnym formacie
* bardzo dobre rozumienie:

• hooków

• retencji uwagi

• dynamiki short-form video
* umiejętność pracy z:

• animowanymi napisami

• efektami i przejściami

• viralowymi dźwiękami (z zachowaniem estetyki marki)
* portfolio (warunek konieczny)

Jesteśmy gotowi na umowę w formie zlecenia projektowego lub godzinowego oraz rozliczenie na bazie projektów lub stawki godzinowej, wcześniej uzgodnionej przed rozpoczęciem pracy.

items.text:
Vicky Boone Casting is looking for a real youth women's Softball team for background roles in an Academy Sports commercial. 
Details below:

Project: Academy Sports
Production Company: The Bear
Project Type:  Social Media Campaign (will run 2 weeks)
Union Status: Non-Union
Project Rate: $250/day per player and coach
Shoot Date(s): January 21-23 OR 22-24, 2026 (will shoot 1 day within this range)
Shoot Location: Austin, TX. Must be local to Austin.

—
We are looking for:
[REAL SOFTBALL TEAM] Girls, ages 11-12. We’re seeking a racially diverse group with team spirit who can bring natural chants, cheers and teamwork. All skill levels are acceptable, but need at least one with a strong swing. Casting 12 players and 1-2 Coaches.

If you and your team might be a fit and are interested in submitting, please submit ASAP to submissions@vickyboonecasting.com by sending the following info:
*Name
*City you and your team are based in
*Contact Number
*Two recent photos (one of you and one of your team)
*Confirm you are avail for all the dates mentioned or list conflicts (1/21-1/23, 1/22-1/24, 2026)
*Please tell us a little bit about your softball team!
*Please use the subject line “SOFTBALL TEAM”

We look forward to your submissions!
Team VBC

sharedPost.text:
Der Kino Mittwoch auf radioYpsilon 

MOVIETIME KW 52/2025

DIE FILMTIPPS  FÜR DAS WEIHNACHTSFEST UND DIE KRAFT DER WAHREN LIEBE 

Nach fast 30jähriger Abstinenz beisst die ANACONDA erneut zu und sorgt nicht nur für gruselige Momente, denn Jack Black ist Garant dafür, daß der Überlebenskampf auch heitere Momente haben kann.

Ins 11. Jahrhunderts verschlägt es uns in der Fortsetzung DER MEDICUS 2 und kurz vor dem Jahresende öffnet das Kronenkino seine Pforten und zeigt den aktuellen Film von Christian Petzold.

Passend zur Sendung am Heiligen Abend erzählt uns Manfred Pawlik über die Liebe zweier Menschen, die auch einen Weg gefunden haben mit einer schweren Krankheit gemeinsam umzugehen.

Weitere Filmtipps und die schönsten Weihnachts Hits,  präsentiert Ihnen unsere Weihnachtselfin, Sarah Fuchs. 

Mittwoch 24.12.25 von 18 bis 19h auf radioYpsilon 94.5 oder via Stream (http://mp3.radioypsilon.at:8000/)

Pop me a message for further info ASAP. ❤️

items.text:
**CASTING & PARTICIPATION CALL – MADE FIGHT LEAGUE™ REALITY SERIES (LAS VEGAS)**

Made Fight League™ is officially recruiting for an upcoming **6-week unscripted reality series** filming in **Las Vegas** in **early 2026** (exact dates TBA).

We are hiring **both UNION and NON-UNION** talent.

This project blends **entertainment, comedy, drama, lifestyle, and competition** inside a **safe, professionally run environment**. It will be **streamed 24/7**, capturing real personalities, real moments, and real opportunity.
WHO WE’RE LOOKING FOR:

• Actors (union & non-union)
• Everyday people with strong personalities
• Athletes & fighters
• Musicians & artists
• Comedians & entertainers
• Creators, performers, and big characters
• Anyone who believes their **experience, resources, or credit** could meaningfully support production is also encouraged to reach out
KEY DETAILS:

• **Location:** Las Vegas
• **Duration:** 6 weeks
• **Ages:** 21–45 (must be 21+)
• **Status:** Paid, role-based participation
• **Travel & lodging:** Provided
• **Daily per diem:** Provided
• **Environment:** Safe, professional, fully managed
• **Format:** Unscripted reality (entertainment, comedy, drama)
• **Exposure:** Major visibility through Made Fight League™ platforms

This is a **career-level opportunity**, not a hobby project. The right participants will gain exposure, content, connections, and real momentum.
HOW TO APPLY:

Email **madefightleague@gmail.com**
**Deadline:** **January 10th**

Please include:
• A short description of who you are
• Why you’d be a strong fit
• Photos **or** social media links (Instagram preferred)

If you’ve ever wanted to be part of something **bigger than a one-off gig**, this is it.

Serious inquiries only.

— **Ashlee Gambino**
Co-Founder, Made Fight League™

• Anyone who believes their **experience, resources, or credit** could meaningfully support production is also encouraged to reach out
KEY DETAILS:

• **Location:** Las Vegas
• **Duration:** 6 weeks
• **Ages:** 21–45 (must be 21+)
• **Status:** Paid, role-based participation
• **Travel & lodging:** Provided
• **Daily per diem:** Provided
• **Environment:** Safe, professional, fully managed
• **Format:** Unscripted reality (entertainment, comedy, drama)
• **Exposure:** Major visibility through Made Fight League™ platforms

This is a **career-level opportunity**, not a hobby project. The right participants will gain exposure, content, connections, and real momentum.
HOW TO APPLY:

Email **madefightleague@gmail.com**
**Deadline:** **January 10th**

Please include:
• A short description of who you are
• Why you’d be a strong fit
• Photos **or** social media links (Instagram preferred)

If you’ve ever wanted to be part of something **bigger than a one-off gig**, this is it.

Serious inquiries only.

— **Ashlee Gambino**
Co-Founder, Made Fight League™

Hey Everyone,

I’m an actor based near Portland, Oregon, with four years of professional experience across film and other media. While I’m often cast in the horror genre, my training and range extend well beyond it, and I actively pursue diverse roles across multiple genres.

I trained for approximately three years primarily in the Meisner technique and continue to strengthen my craft through ongoing improv work. My projects have filmed in Los Angeles, on the East Coast, and internationally, including the feature film Irish Ashes, shot in the UK.

I’m open to a wide range of roles and characters and am fully available for both domestic and international travel.

[https://youtu.be/4UGclq-Ux4Q](https://youtu.be/4UGclq-Ux4Q)

## **🎭 CASTING CALL — TALKING MIME (WHITEFACE)**

**Mini Sessions | Non-Union | Ages 35–45**

Hi everyone — we’re **RETROcirq Studios, LLC**, a small, human-produced media studio creating short-form, nostalgia-inspired content for YouTube.

Our current project, **Studio 3**, is a curated channel inspired by classic late-night TV, UHF programming, and retro media. It’s designed to feel like something you *drop into* — short segments, odd interstitials, and occasional performances.

**This is not a scripted series and not a cast-driven show.**

**🎭 WHAT WE’RE CASTING**

We’re looking for **one non-union female performer (ages 35–45)** for **short mini-sessions** as a **talking mime**.

These are brief on-camera appearances used as:

* bumpers
* short segments
* interstitial moments

Each appearance runs approximately **30–90 seconds**.

**📌 BOOKING, SCOPE & OUR COMMITMENT**

This role is booked **one session at a time**.

Any additional sessions, if offered, are determined later based on project needs and are **not guaranteed**.

**What we do promise:**

* Clear communication
* Fair compensation, paid on time
* Transparency about each booking
* No surprises or implied obligations

If additional sessions are offered, they will always be discussed openly and confirmed in advance.

**PERFORMANCE DETAILS**

* Light dialogue combined with expressive facial/physical performance
* Calm, grounded delivery (restraint over theatrics)
* Comfortable speaking directly to camera
* Comfortable working in a small, flexible production environment

👉 **Mime experience is NOT required.**

Strong on-camera presence and facial expressiveness matter more than formal mime training.

**🎨 MAKEUP REQUIREMENT**

* **Classic whiteface mime makeup**
   * Clean white base
   * Simple black accents (eyes, brows, mouth)
   * No prosthetics
   * No elaborate or theatrical designs

Whiteface is used strictly as **visual shorthand**, not character lore.

**❌ THIS IS NOT**

* A series lead
* A guaranteed recurring role
* A long-term commitment
* An influencer or branding opportunity

**🎬 AUDITION**

* 30–60 second self-tape
* Neutral background
* Simple wardrobe
* **Whiteface makeup applied**
* One short prompt (shared privately)

**💵 COMPENSATION**

* **$150 flat per session**
* Booked one session at a time
* Additional sessions not guaranteed

* **Non-union performers only**

RETROcirq Studios is intentionally small and human-first.

We value clarity, flexibility, respectful collaboration, and low drama.

If you’re looking for something lightweight, creative, and clearly defined — with honest communication — this may be a good fit.

Performer acknowledges that this project is **produced remotely**. Performer will record footage from their own location using their own equipment (smartphone or camera acceptable) following general technical guidelines provided by Producer. No travel, studio access, or in-person production is required or implied.

**Interested?**

Please comment **“interested”** and **DM us** for audition details.

**Quick notes:**

• $150 flat per session (not negotiable)

• Non-union only

• Ages 35–45

• Whiteface makeup required

• Booked one session at a time; additional sessions not guaranteed

• We promise clear communication and fair pay for every session

The goal is to improve their facial filters. It pays **$350** for approximately **2.5 hours** of participation in **Los Angeles**.

If interested, please sign up using the form below:

I've participated in the study myself and was able to complete it in an hour! Feel free to check out our Instagram @danbellcasting or call the office if you have any questions.

🎭 **Jetzt Schauspiel entdecken – bequem von zu Hause!**

Der **Schauspiel-Kompaktkurs** der Schauspielwerkstatt Berlin startet **am 19. Januar 2026**.

6 Wochen – live via ZOOM – ideal für **Anfänger/innen & Schauspielinteressierte**, die endlich einsteigen wollen.

Was du bekommst:
• lebendige Schauspielgrundlagen
• Ausdrucks- & Präsenztraining
• Szenenarbeit in einer motivierten Gruppe
• professionelles Feedback

Nice to know: Die Effektivität von strukturiertem Online-Live-Coaching ist gut untersucht, z. B. laut Digital Education Action Plan der EU.

items.text:
🎬 HELP WANTED — ALIEN INVASION MIXTURE (Volunteer Sci‑Fi Series)

Hi! My name is Liam, and I’m creating a youth‑led sci‑fi action series called Alien Invasion Mixture. It follows three powerful female heroes — Maria, Laterally, and Jamie — whose music unlocks their weapons and summons their allies as they defend their world from King Burial and his alien forces.

The universe is protected by a massive cosmic shield called The Holo.
The Holo has no cracks — instead, it is powered by the fans who support Starwave. Their energy keeps the shield alive. Aliens can invade in small numbers, but most are blocked. When the heroes seal The Holo with their music, it becomes completely impenetrable, protecting their world from King Burial and all alien threats.

---

⭐ IMPORTANT: This is a volunteer project

All roles are unpaid.
This series is being made for fun, experience, and portfolio building.
Everyone who joins participates voluntarily, and I (Liam) am the creator and owner of the project.

---

🎤 No voice acting required

To keep characters consistent:

• All voices will be done using AI voice tools
• Volunteers do not need to record dialogue
• Different actors can play the same character without changing the voice

---

🎥 How recording works (NO studio needed)

You don’t need a studio, special equipment, or costumes.

Here’s the process:

• I send you the movements or scenes to record
• You record at home using your phone
• You send the footage back to me
• I convert your performance into animated characters using motion capture and digital backgrounds

Anyone can help from anywhere.

---

👥 Who I’m looking for

• Motion capture actors
• People who want to help behind the scenes
• Anyone who enjoys sci‑fi, animation, or creative projects
• Family and friends are welcome to join too

---

🎤 Why join?

• Fun, creative, and flexible
• Great for building experience
• Help from home
• No costumes or voice acting needed
• You’ll be credited in the series
• Be part of a unique music‑powered sci‑fi universe

---

If you’re interested, message me or comment below. I’ll send character options, movement instructions, and more details about the world of Alien Invasion Mixture. I’d love to have you join the team and help bring this universe to life.

sharedPost.text:
Breaking news! 

Making Contact
Two last-minute places have just come available!! 

Looking for:
One male-identifying actor
One female-identifying actor

Course sold out quickly so jump in while you have a chance. This is the only extensive actor training of its type in London.

Making Contact is a twelve-week physical theatre workshop that asks:

How do performers make contact?
How is it managed?
How do actors prepare for physical, violent and intimate scenes -  not just manage them, but take joy in the process?
How can actors break habits of hesitation and meet physical work with confidence, play and freedom?

This playful yet practical training offers a safe, yet brave space to build confidence, clarity and skill in physical connection. The work centres consent and boundary setting while encouraging curiosity, physical play and embodied listening.

Participants explore dynamic practices including gameplay, contact improvisation and shared weight work, designed to support actors in working physically with trust and enjoyment. Scenes involving intimacy, violence and imaginary relationships are approached with care, rigour and professionalism.

Led by a certified fight and intimacy director with over 30 years’ international experience, Making Contact is ideal for actors who want to:
– establish clear, healthy boundaries
– move beyond hesitation around physical contact
– extend their physical range and availability
– approach intimacy and violence with confidence, care and joy

The training provides practical tools for theatre and film while fostering trust, openness and pleasure in the craft.

Participants will explore:
– industry standards in intimacy and consent
– mental and physical preparation for the work
– quality boundary setting
– physical exploration and gameplay
– contact improvisation and shared weight
– exploration of theatrical violence
– engagement in imaginary relationships under physical circumstances
– body preparation and physical / mental closure
– final performances of fully coordinated and directed scenes

📅 Jan 10 – March 28, 2026
⏱ 12 weeks | In-person | London
💰 £450 (deposit options available)

www.bodymindvoice.co.uk

Filmmakers!! 🚨

We need broadcast-ready, distribution-ready independent films and series.
Work that’s finished.
Work that’s polished.
Work that deserves a proper audience.
We’re creating a home where: 🎬 High-quality independent cinema is curated, not buried

And you get paid direct from the audience! No more middle men and gatekeeping and no more getting screwed by Film Hub, Tubi, Netflix and poor Youtube monetisation.

We have over 1500 people on our waiting list and We’re in the final phase now to change self distribution forever!

We are also looking for beta testers, to start testing out the app and site prelaunch, whilst films are curated and rolled into the library.

👉 Join the waiting list now: www.indiecrib.com

Let’s prove that great stories don’t need Hollywood’s permission.
Welcome to the crib 🎬 🏠

🚨 Launching very soon. 🚨
Indie Crib is almost live and we’re opening film & series submissions in the coming weeks.
This isn’t a platform for rough cuts or half-finished ideas.
Indie Crib is built for broadcast-ready, distribution-ready independent films and series.
Work that’s finished.
Work that’s polished.
Work that deserves a proper audience.
We’re creating a home where: 🎬 High-quality independent cinema is curated, not buried

🎬 Films and series are discovered intentionally, not by algorithm chaos
🎬 Filmmakers are treated like professionals, not content farms
If you’ve made something you believe in and you’re ready for it to stand on its own, this is for you.

We have over 1500 people on our waiting list and We’re in the final phase now to change self distribution forever!

Doors open very soon.
Independent cinema.
Discovered differently. 

— Aeman
Founder, Indie Crib

Thanks!

items.text:
''They got me an apartment in New York!''

She was close to tears on our zoom call.

''And the flight's paid for too! I even get a per diem of $100 a day! 
That's on top of what they pay me and it's A LOT, KC!''

After she got over the thrill of booking a recurring role on a series (in NY!!!) her mind was blown about everything else that came with it. 

She'd put almost 5 years of constant study with me to get to this level and she took absolutely none of it for granted. 

It was a lot of work and the work didn't stop when she got to NY. 

18 hour days.
Incredibly challenging scenes (I wish I could tell you because it's mind-blowing what she did but I can't).
Living in a country where she knew no one.

An since that series she's continued to work hard and book. 

It doesn't get easier when you find success. The challenges are different. 

You can start now and put in the work and build the muscles that help you meet those challenges. 

Or you can look back in 5 years from now and think I wish I did it. 

Regret is an ugly thing to live with. 

I have a few, but as the song goes, too few to mention. 

Donna-Marie Manning and I are very selective about who we work with. 

Your success is our success. 

We don't have these stories to tell if you don't book. So we only want to work with committed and dedicated actors.

When you fill out this form tell us everything. 

https://form.jotform.com/253125203574248

We promise we won't laugh at you or judge you for wanting to act. 

We know people sometimes do. We don't. 

Our job is helping actors make their dreams come true. 

Don't hold back. We need to know you to coach you. 

xo KC

 • Height: 183 cm+

⸻

⸻

items.text:
KIARA’S PSALM

**** Filming in Charlotte, NC area in 2026'****

CASTING CALL OF VARIOUS DEMOGRAPHICS 

ALL roles 📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, contact info and reels(if reels are available) to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com 

**Casting now. Don't delay** 

Feature Film | Drama / Music / Thriller

Produced by K-Latt Studios

🎤 CASTING: KIARA LANGSTON (LEAD)

Female | Early to late 20s| African American

A once-rising singer silenced by trauma. A voice the world never forgot.

We are seeking a powerful actress with exceptional singing ability to portray Kiara—a woman reclaiming her voice after tragedy.

✨ Strong vocalist required

✨ Emotional depth & screen presence essential

✨ Star power encouraged

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, reel & singing clips to

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Kiara

🛡️ CASTING: ELIAS CARTER (MALE LEAD)

Male | Early 30s–Late 40s | Open Ethnicity

A highly trained bodyguard. Calm. Protective. Unshakeable.

Elias is strength wrapped in restraint—and the unexpected safe place for a wounded soul.

✨ Strong physically attractive dramatic actor

✨ Subtle, grounded romantic chemistry required

✨ Physically believable, emotionally controlled

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Elias

💛 CASTING: JANESSA REED

Female | 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity 

Best friend. Protector. Truth-teller.

Janessa is the emotional backbone of Kiara’s world—fierce, loving, and unwavering.

✨ Natural charisma

✨ Strong dialogue delivery

✨ Emotionally intelligent performance

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Janessa

🎧 CASTING: DEREK MORRIS

Male | 30s–40s | Open Ethnicity

A trusted member of Kiara’s inner circle.

Derek handles business, security, and hard truths when emotions run high.

✨ Professional presence

✨ Strong supporting performance

✨ Grounded realism

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Derek

🏔️ CASTING: MOTHER CARTER

Female | 60s to 70s | Open Ethnicity

Warm. Watchful. Protective.

The quiet heart of a secluded mountain home offering refuge—and concern.

✨ Subtle, expressive acting

✨ Strong presence with minimal dialogue

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Mother Carter

🪵 CASTING: FATHER CARTER

Male | 60s–70s | Open Ethnicity

A man of principle and restraint.

Protective of his home, wary of danger, loyal to his son.

✨ Controlled, grounded performance

✨ Emotional depth through silence

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Father Carter

🕶️ CASTING: THE OBSESSED FAN (ANTAGONIST)

Male | Late 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity

Charming. Obsessive. Dangerous.

This role requires psychological realism, not theatrics.

⚠️ Dark, nuanced character

✨ Subtle menace & emotional control

✨ Comfort portraying unsettling behavior

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – The Fan

🎙️ CASTING: JOURNALIST / INTERVIEWER

Male or Female | 30s–50s | Open Ethnicity

Poised. Perceptive. Respectful.

The Journalist is the voice guiding Kiara’s story—conducting the interview that frames the film and gently draws out her past, her pain, and her truth. This character must balance professionalism with empathy, knowing when to press and when to listen.

✨ Strong on-camera presence

✨ Natural conversational delivery

✨ Ability to convey depth through listening and subtle reactions

✨ Broadcast or documentary-style experience a plus

This role anchors key emotional moments and requires restraint, intelligence, and authenticity.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Journalist

🧠 CASTING: THERAPIST

Male or Female | 40s–60s | Open Ethnicity

Calm. Grounded. Steady.

The Therapist is a safe space—someone who helps Kiara confront trauma without judgment or pressure. This character doesn’t rescue or lecture; they listen, guide, and gently challenge. Their presence allows Kiara to begin reclaiming her voice.

✨ Deep emotional intelligence

✨ Strong listening and reaction skills

✨ Subtle, naturalistic performance style

✨ Ability to convey warmth, patience, and trust

This role requires restraint, authenticity, and a deep respect for trauma-informed storytelling.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Therapist

🌿 CASTING: MARILYN

Female | 40s–60s | African American

Warm. Faith-filled. Steady.

Marilyn is a gentle presence in Kiara’s life —functioning as both mom and manager, she is someone who knew her before the fame, before the trauma. Rooted in faith and wisdom, Marilyn represents unconditional love, spiritual grounding, and the reminder of who Kiara was before the world broke her.

She speaks dynamically but with purpose. Her words linger. Some singing ability is needed.

✨ Nurturing yet strong presence

✨ Natural, grounded performance

✨ Ability to convey spiritual depth without preaching

✨ Comfort portraying quiet emotional moments

This role is large in impact.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Marilyn 

These are All PAID roles for this feature film. 

GOOD LUCK! See you on set! 

K-latt Studios

items.summary:
KIARA’S PSALM

**** Filming in Charlotte, NC area in 2026'****

CASTING CALL OF VARIOUS DEMOGRAPHICS 

ALL roles 📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, contact info and reels(if reels are available) to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com 

**Casting now. Don't delay** 

Feature Film | Drama / Music / Thriller

Produced by K-Latt Studios

🎤 CASTING: KIARA LANGSTON (LEAD)

Female | Early to late 20s| African American

A once-rising singer silenced by trauma. A voice the world never forgot.

We are seeking a powerful actress with exceptional singing ability to portray Kiara—a woman reclaiming her voice after tragedy.

✨ Strong vocalist required

✨ Emotional depth & screen presence essential

✨ Star power encouraged

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, reel & singing clips to

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Kiara

🛡️ CASTING: ELIAS CARTER (MALE LEAD)

Male | Early 30s–Late 40s | Open Ethnicity

A highly trained bodyguard. Calm. Protective. Unshakeable.

Elias is strength wrapped in restraint—and the unexpected safe place for a wounded soul.

✨ Strong physically attractive dramatic actor

✨ Subtle, grounded romantic chemistry required

✨ Physically believable, emotionally controlled

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Elias

💛 CASTING: JANESSA REED

Female | 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity 

Best friend. Protector. Truth-teller.

Janessa is the emotional backbone of Kiara’s world—fierce, loving, and unwavering.

✨ Natural charisma

✨ Strong dialogue delivery

✨ Emotionally intelligent performance

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Janessa

🎧 CASTING: DEREK MORRIS

Male | 30s–40s | Open Ethnicity

A trusted member of Kiara’s inner circle.

Derek handles business, security, and hard truths when emotions run high.

✨ Professional presence

✨ Strong supporting performance

✨ Grounded realism

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Derek

🏔️ CASTING: MOTHER CARTER

Female | 60s to 70s | Open Ethnicity

Warm. Watchful. Protective.

The quiet heart of a secluded mountain home offering refuge—and concern.

✨ Subtle, expressive acting

✨ Strong presence with minimal dialogue

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Mother Carter

🪵 CASTING: FATHER CARTER

Male | 60s–70s | Open Ethnicity

A man of principle and restraint.

Protective of his home, wary of danger, loyal to his son.

✨ Controlled, grounded performance

✨ Emotional depth through silence

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Father Carter

🕶️ CASTING: THE OBSESSED FAN (ANTAGONIST)

Male | Late 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity

Charming. Obsessive. Dangerous.

This role requires psychological realism, not theatrics.

⚠️ Dark, nuanced character

✨ Subtle menace & emotional control

✨ Comfort portraying unsettling behavior

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – The Fan

🎙️ CASTING: JOURNALIST / INTERVIEWER

Male or Female | 30s–50s | Open Ethnicity

Poised. Perceptive. Respectful.

The Journalist is the voice guiding Kiara’s story—conducting the interview that frames the film and gently draws out her past, her pain, and her truth. This character must balance professionalism with empathy, knowing when to press and when to listen.

✨ Strong on-camera presence

✨ Natural conversational delivery

✨ Ability to convey depth through listening and subtle reactions

✨ Broadcast or documentary-style experience a plus

This role anchors key emotional moments and requires restraint, intelligence, and authenticity.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Journalist

🧠 CASTING: THERAPIST

Male or Female | 40s–60s | Open Ethnicity

Calm. Grounded. Steady.

The Therapist is a safe space—someone who helps Kiara confront trauma without judgment or pressure. This character doesn’t rescue or lecture; they listen, guide, and gently challenge. Their presence allows Kiara to begin reclaiming her voice.

✨ Deep emotional intelligence

✨ Strong listening and reaction skills

✨ Subtle, naturalistic performance style

✨ Ability to convey warmth, patience, and trust

This role requires restraint, authenticity, and a deep respect for trauma-informed storytelling.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Therapist

🌿 CASTING: MARILYN

Female | 40s–60s | African American

Warm. Faith-filled. Steady.

Marilyn is a gentle presence in Kiara’s life —functioning as both mom and manager, she is someone who knew her before the fame, before the trauma. Rooted in faith and wisdom, Marilyn represents unconditional love, spiritual grounding, and the reminder of who Kiara was before the world broke her.

She speaks dynamically but with purpose. Her words linger. Some singing ability is needed.

✨ Nurturing yet strong presence

✨ Natural, grounded performance

✨ Ability to convey spiritual depth without preaching

✨ Comfort portraying quiet emotional moments

This role is large in impact.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Marilyn 

These are All PAID roles for this feature film. 

GOOD LUCK! See you on set! 

K-latt Studios

items.text:
We are casting for an updated tour of the children’s theatre show, “The Dinosaur That Pooped a Rock Show”, based on the popular books by McFly’s Tom Fletcher and Dougie Poynter. 

The show is written and directed by Miranda Larson with songs and music by Tom Fletcher & Dougie Poynter and Barrie Bignold and is produced by Mark Thompson at MT Productions. 

**Production dates:**

Auditions will take place on 24th November 2025

Rehearsals begin on 12th January – 22nd January 2026 in London
Tour dates Jan – Nov 2026.
We are currently have 91 dates and counting. 

**Production location: **Greater London

**Role: **We are looking for a costume character/ skin artist to play the role of Dino. The artist will need to operate Dino’s mouth, hands and head, bringing the character to life. They will also be required to join in dance moves and routines whilst inside the costume. We are looking for someone between 5’6” and 5’10” tall. Previous skin/ costume character experience is essential.

The successful applicant will need to have a full UK drivers licence and will be comfortable driving the touring van on a shared basis with the rest of the company.

Please send CV's & headshots to: casting.mtproductions@gmail.com

**Fees:**

Rehearsal fee: £550pw

Show day fee: £150

Travel day fee: £50

Subsistence: £20

AUDITONS FOR RAG DOLLY - THE RAGGEDY ANN MUSICAL WORKSHOP 

Seeking actors for a public workshop reading of Rag Dolly. Come aboard our cast and our bed-boat as we sail through Mexico up to LA to cure a broken heart! Look for actors, singers, dancers, non singers and youth actors. 

RAGGEDY ANN WANTS YOU TO AUDITION!

In Rag Dolly, a little girl named Marcella is dying of a mysterious illness. Her father makes her a rag doll to comfort her, and his stories of the doll come to life in her dreams to guide her through her grief and fear. Marcella and her new friends confront wolves, witches, and incompetent doctors on their way to outwit death and mend her broken heart.

items.text:
PURPLE DREAMS PRODUCTIONS are looking for several performers to join a few projects, primarily our brand new family-friendly play: 

THE PRINCESS & THE KNIGHT

a fantasy play written by Tobias Nicholls

Welcome to Twinklewood, a fantastical land where darkness and light have lived in harmony for decades… until now.

Whilst the King is away on a royal tour, the Ruler of the Shadow Realm makes an unexpected appearance. Sir Milo is determined to keep his princess safe, but with her Kingdom thrown into chaos, Princess Nova - who has long dreamt of adventure - springs into action, taking them on a journey up to the highest mountain and down to the deepest, darkest cave.

Battles are fought and lessons learned on this funny and exciting quest.  

This brand new production is set to debut at The Seagull Theatre in Lowestoft on Saturday 4th April 2026

Two performances on the one day as a tester before we look at booking any others. 

The script is currently going through a rewrite, with the intention to have the cast help to develop the characters through the rehearsal process with the director. 

Adding to the fantastical nature of the story, the characters of Twinklewood will all feature likenesses to animals - realised through costume and make-up.  Aside from one, roles have not been assigned any particular animal, allowing the chosen actors can help build their character.

Payment: at this stage of development it’s best to consider this a profit share, although this could change to a flat fee - happy to have open and honest discussions with applicants. 

Rehearsals will take place at our studio in Hunstanton (PE36), and will be as flexible as possible to fit around other commitments.

If you are interested, or know someone that might be, please get in touch via a DM on here, or email purple-dreams@hotmail.co.uk

Hello! I’m one of the producers at Pipmonk, a London-based production company. Our team is now casting the female lead role in ‘Framed Between Two’. We are looking for a Chinese / British-Chinese female aged 25-30. Please note the ability to speak both English and Cantonese language is required. Please see more details in the attachment below.

Contact email: 

framedbetweentwo.movie@gmail.com

(To clear up any confusion: you may have seen the casting call for our male lead circulating, which mentions a Hong Kong unit. Please note that our female lead is needed for the London unit ONLY, as she does not have any scenes in Hong Kong.)

Thanks!

message.text:
Togetherness & Christmas... 
May it be as calm and full of warm lights as it can be. 

Merry Christmas. 

SONGS FROM LIFE  is about togetherness. 
It plays on January 10th at 20:00 at the Gallus Theater Frankfurt.
Tickets: https://www.gallustheater.de/prog/vob.php?i=27

In February and March the show will to Adelaide and Newcastle, Australia.

#lights #togetherness #christmas #zagrebchristmasmarket
#stefanierrummel1 @adlfringe @newcastlefringe @estillvoice

items.text:
How Script Analysis Changes Everything About Your Auditions

Most auditions aren’t lost because of talent — they’re lost because of uncertainty.

When actors don’t fully understand what their character wants, why they want it, or how they’re trying to get it, that confusion shows up instantly on camera. Lines feel disconnected. Emotional beats feel random. Choices feel hesitant instead of intentional. And casting directors stop watching.

This video breaks down how Script & Scene Analysis inside MyAuditionAI.com removes that uncertainty before the camera ever turns on.

Instead of guessing or overthinking, actors upload their script and receive a professional breakdown of objectives, obstacles, tactics, and emotional beats using proven acting techniques. The result is clarity — and clarity is what makes performances easy to follow and easy to say yes to.

Actors who book consistently aren’t guessing.
They’re prepared.

👉 Stop guessing. Start preparing with clarity.

Visit MyAuditionAI.com and start your 7-day free trial today.

items.text:
I made an AI video to advertise my acting classes…

It was so bad it actually reassured me. 😭😂

Actors — you’re safe.
But more importantly…

If you’ve ever thought:
👉 “I’d love to act but I’m probably not good enough”
👉 “I’ve left it too late”
👉 “People like me don’t get into this industry”

That’s exactly who our classes are for.

You don’t need confidence.
You don’t need experience.
You don’t need to be “ready”.

You just need a space where:
🎭 You’re allowed to try
🎭 You’re shown how
🎭 You’re given real tools
🎭 You’re supported by people doing the work

January classes are open.
🎬 Free trial available

Come see if this is where your acting journey starts.

👉 Book your FREE trial
🔗 linktr.ee/mattzina

message.text:
I made an AI video to advertise my acting classes…

It was so bad it actually reassured me. 😭😂

Actors — you’re safe.
But more importantly…

If you’ve ever thought:
👉 “I’d love to act but I’m probably not good enough”
👉 “I’ve left it too late”
👉 “People like me don’t get into this industry”

That’s exactly who our classes are for.

You don’t need confidence.
You don’t need experience.
You don’t need to be “ready”.

You just need a space where:
🎭 You’re allowed to try
🎭 You’re shown how
🎭 You’re given real tools
🎭 You’re supported by people doing the work

January classes are open.
🎬 Free trial available

Come see if this is where your acting journey starts.

👉 Book your FREE trial
🔗 linktr.ee/mattzina

I have reduced the cost of the full course (4 sessions) for December, so you can buy as a gift, or just get it for yourself 😄

Running at Friargate Theatre in York on Sunday mornings in January, this is the perfect way to grasp the lessons taught in all drama schools, and put them into practice. Full details on the website:

January Acting course at Friargate Theatre now on sale! 

And I have reduced the price of the whole course for December for all your gifting (or self gifting) needs! 

Beat the January blues by having a wonderful group of performers to enjoy acting with, or give someone that boost into performance they keep talking about doing. 

Follow the link to our website for full details: "Foundation in Professional Acting"

#actingclass #whatsoninyork #theatre #york #january2026 #friargatetheatre #actinglessons

items.summary:
I have reduced the cost of the full course (4 sessions) for December, so you can buy as a gift, or just get it for yourself 😄

Running at Friargate Theatre in York on Sunday mornings in January, this is the perfect way to grasp the lessons taught in all drama schools, and put them into practice. Full details on the website:

Lisbeth Salander type søges: Ulønnet.

Til testoptagelser i Marts/April 2026. 

Til udvikling af et kommende projekt der desværre stadig er ret hemmeligt, søges en Lisbeth Salander type. 

Der er tale om testoptagelser der er enten vil komme til at foregå i Aarhus eller København, alt efter individuel aftale. Opgaven tager max 3 timer. 
 
Du skal være åben for et længere samarbejde hvis du udvælges til at være en af de skuespillere vi vil fortsætte projektet med. 

Derfor SKAL du tage disse ting i betragtning inden du søger rollen. 

Krav til rollen: 

Du skal have skuespiller erfaring.
Du skal være i god form.
Du skal være åben for ideen om at portrættere en bisexual karakter. 
Du skal være åben for at lave kampscener og blive trænet i kamp koreografi af vores stunt coordinator. 
 
Lyder dette som noget for dig så send en ansøgning hvor du fortæller lidt om dig selv. Husk at inkludere opdaterede billeder samt alder og højde.
Alle er velkomne til at søge uanset etnicitet og alder. Men som udgangspunkt skal du minimum være fyldt 18år.

Alle ansøgninger skal sendes via email til:

brook_lynmarvin@hotmail.com

Deadline for ansøgning er d.20/2.2026.
Vi svarer kun på dem vi er interesseret i at bruge og der svares ikke på henvendelser via messenger eller i kommentarfeltet.

Hallo an alle! 

Wenn jemand Lust hat mal bei einem Kurzfilm mitzuspielen, now’s your chance! Im Rahmen eines Semesterprojekts an der FH St Pölten suchen wir Schauspieler, die am 4. und 5.1. 2026 bei einem 10 minütigen Kurzfilm mitspielen wollen! 

Erfahrung ist nicht notwendig, aber von Vorteil

Wir brauchen folgende Rollen: 

Hauptdarsteller (m, 19-24)

Job Interviewer (m, 20+)

Sprecherin  (w, 20+)

Bei Interesse bitte bei mir privat melden! 

Gage können wir leider keine bieten.

Ich freu mich auf alle, die mitwirken wollen!

items.text:
Warmest Holiday Wishes from Our Creative Family to Yours!

As the season blankets Colorado and 2025 draws to a close, we at S.E.B. Casting, CSA want to take a moment to thank you for being part of our vibrant community of performers, directors, producers, advertisers, agents and creative visionaries. Your talent and passion continue to inspire us every day.

A Year of Breakthrough Performances
2025 has been extraordinary for the S.E.B. Casting community. From launching careers in award-winning productions to connecting diverse talent with innovative projects, we've watched with pride as performers have shined in everything from national commercials and viral ad campaigns to feature length films. Your commitment to authentic storytelling has helped productions across Colorado and beyond create more inclusive, powerful productions.

What's New at S.E.B.
We're thrilled to announce our studio expansion will be complete in January 2026! This means a more comofrtable audition space, improved casting facilities, and a dedicated area for talent and production. Plus, our Commitment to the Community will continue to grow, lifting individuals, groups. organizations and our whole state as a vibrant, positive, engaging, equitable hub for media arts and artists. 

Holiday Self-Care for Performers:
The holidays can be both magical and hectic for creative professionals. Here are our top tips to stay centered and ready for opportunities in the new year:

Schedule downtime: Block specific days for complete rest - no auditions, no rehearsals, no networking

Stay vocally healthy: Maintain your instrument with extra hydration and vocal rest during holiday gatherings

Update materials: Use the quiet period between December 20-January 5 to refresh headshots, reels, and resumes

Connect authentically: Attend industry gatherings not just for networking, but to genuinely celebrate the season with your creative community 

Here's to New Beginnings!
As we wrap up 2025, we're filled with gratitude for this remarkable community. The new year promises exciting productions, fresh opportunities, and continued growth for Colorado's vibrant media arts scene. Whether you're a seasoned professional or just beginning your journey, know that S.E.B. Casting, CSA is here to champion your unique voice and talent.

*Crown of Blood* is a powerful Yoruba reimagining of **Macbeth**, rooted in our history, ritual, language, music and kingship traditions. This is not just a play. It is our stories, our power and our worldview on one of the UK’s most prestigious stages.

📍 Crucible Theatre, Sheffield
📅 2–7 February 2026

Please support this work by buying tickets, sharing widely and encouraging friends and family to attend. Representation only grows when we show up for it.

🎟️ Tickets here:
[https://www.sheffieldtheatres.co.uk/events/crown-of-blood](https://www.sheffieldtheatres.co.uk/events/crown-of-blood)

Seeking extras for LGBT Sci - Fi feature.

We are shooting a stunt based scene for a Sci Fi feature film.

This is one of our last shoots and the film is scheduled to be released early next year 

 

We have a professional stunt coordinator and stunt man and the scene involves a homeless man being set on fire.

Every safety caution will me met and we even will have a medic to evaluate all health and safety of the seton the day.

You would plan a gang of rowdy people who attack the homeless man. Great featured part and you would witness a cool live stunt and get full credits in the film and IMDb.

Due to the location being on a farm it would be preferable that you drive as public transport would be tricky.

You will be needed for maximum two hours and it pays a flat fee of £30 and we can also pay your travel /fuel

 

Date is 5th of January in Bridgnorth

 

Get in touch for all info and details via PM

or email luxkapsaski@gmail.com

topComments.text: I can help you there! Only up the road from me. 54 year old White man with beard. SA experience!

I am Thomas Goersch from Stuttgart Germany. 
Actor and Filmdirector. 
I am making Independent Movies and some kind of Art House Underground Movies. I present my movies on International Film festivals and was lucky to receive some awards. 
But the work is not about awards and money, its about making movies for the people to think about.
My next movie is a modern love story:
An elderly man is meeting another younger, very attractive man in the Internet.  But they are from different Continents. They start a long distance relastionship ship. which is full of passion and desire. 
One day the younger man starts to ask for money, cause he is a Student and no more able to pay his bills. 
The older man is full of distrust.
Is he only there  to pay his lovers bills or is there love between them ?
A story with two endings.
One with true love and one with betrayl.

I am looking for the young attraktive Lover.
Men  25 to 42 years old,  good looking  who is able to film his parts on his own by smartshone
I am always open and honest. You can earn no money on this. but maybe there is a good film in the end promoting for you.
I guess its not necessary that an educated actor is playing this part. so feel free to get in touch

Thats me 
www.imdb.com/name/nm1591928

Get in touch under Thomas.Goersch@vodafonemail.de 

please ask for details.

Hello! I’m one of the producers at Pipmonk, a London-based production company. Our team is now casting the female lead role in ‘Framed Between Two’. We are looking for a Chinese / British-Chinese female aged 25-30. Please note the ability to speak both English and Cantonese language is required. Please see more details in the attachment below.

Contact email: 

framedbetweentwo.movie@gmail.com

(To clear up any confusion: you may have seen the casting call for our male lead circulating, which mentions a Hong Kong unit. Please note that our female lead is needed for the London unit ONLY, as she does not have any scenes in Hong Kong.)

Thanks!

items.title: NOGET FOR DIG ELLER NOGLE DU KENDER ???

items.text:
Søges: Skuespillere til kortfilm der skal optages henover sommeren 2026. Ulønnet.

Da jeg går med en lille vision om at bryde ud som director efter flere år som skuespiller i tv og film branchen. Har jeg endelig fået skrevet en af mine mange historier færdig, men da jeg gerne vil bryde lidt med normen så skiller dette projekt sig ud da det bogstaveligt er en silent montage film, sat til klassikeren "Nisi Dominus" af Vivaldi. 

Vores working title er indtil videre "The Mafia burial".
Filmen vil vare ca 20min og og vil indeholde en del slow motion og koreograferede blodige action shots. 

Kort synopsis: En respekteret Mafia boss har mistet sit et og alt, nemlig hans datter. Historien starter på en kirkegård hvor vi overværer hendes begravelse, med en hysterisk grædende mor, en masse sørgende håndlangere og mange kondolerende gæster. Iblandt håndlangerne står vores hoved karakter. Da vi zoomer tættere på ham ser vi ham smide en lille tåre, det der skiller ham ud er dog at det er mere end bare sorg vi kan se i ham, han er lige så knust som familien da han var datterens hemmelige elsker. Da vi zoomer mere ind på ham breaker vi over i hans tanker i form af en montage. Hvor vi ser ham eliminere og afhøre flere kriminelle i jagten på hans kærestes morder. Alt dette vil lede op til begravelsen. Der vil komme små brud imellem hans voldelige handlinger hvor han slår over til de små gode kærligheds stunder han havde med hende.

Der skildres imellem en tone af film som The Godfather og Drive. 

Da det hele basically er en silent movie så har vi også valgt at tage os ekstra god tid til at finde de helt rigtige skuespillere til projektet da der her udelukkende skal arbejdes med udtryk og mimik. 
Musikken som vil drive filmen vil være et mix af "Nisi Dominus" af Vivaldi samt nogle andre klassiske stykker. Det hele skydes rundt omkring i Midtjylland henover sommeren 2026, men laves til at ligne et mørkt amerikansk drama. 

Dette er et komplet passion projekt så det hele er ulønnet. Men der vil være forplejning og god stemning på alle set.

Action scener vil være koreograferet og vi arbejder efter et koncept hvor vi prøver at få så meget som muligt ud af så lidt som muligt mht til vinkler close ups and so on. 

Nogle af jer har nok set dette opslag i andre grupper og vi havde egentlig først tænkt os at begynde at caste skuespillere om en måneds tid. Men da rigtig mange af jer allerede har henvendt jer i håb om at udfylde en af de mange roller så kommer vores rolle liste her. 

Rolle...... (Alder)

Mafia Don, Marlon Brando vs John Turturro type(40-65)

Grieving Mafia mom, smuk sydlandsk look men skal kunne udtrykke ekstrem sorg og raseri (30-50)

Mafia Princess, sydlandsk look skal kunne udstråle positivt, hun er nemlig ikke som resten af hendes familie og er det eneste positive vores hovedrolle havde i sit liv (20-30)

The boyfriend, en Ryan gosling/Tom Hardy type(25-40) Hovedrollen, du skal være klar på at lave små stunts og planlagte koreograferede fight sekvenser.

Bodyguard 1,2. Vores Mafia families personlige bodyguards klædt i sort sammen med vores hoved karakter. (30-50)

Bad guy 1,2,3,4,5 (20-40) I skal også være klar på at lave koreograferede fight sekvenser sammen med vores hovedrolle. 

Hitman, en fremhævet bad guy der vil komme til at være mål for vores hovedrolles hævntogt (30-50)

The other Don, en fremhævet Mafia boss der sammen med sin egen familie vil være til stede under begravelsen og være fremhævet som kondolerende (40-65).

Statister:

1) Der skal bruges statister under begravelsen, folk klædt i komplet sorte American style funeral outfits. 
Her skal vi bruge ca 10stk. Alder underordnet, der er dog plads til en ung statist også da vi godt kunne tænke os at se et barn til stede under begravelsen, som spiller et evt familiemedlem.

2) Der skal bruges statister i baggrunden på nogle af vores flashbacks til vores karakterers kærlighed stunder. Her skal vi bruge ca 8 personer med amerikansk hverdags look til små optagelser i bla en park og evt Tivoli. 

3) Flygtende gæster, når vores hovedrolle konfronterer vores bad guys i en dinner, skal vi bruge ca 4 statister til at være gæster i dinneren. 
Her skal man være klar på at få lidt fake blod på sig og evt smide lidt med tingene, da vi laver et slow motion shot der skal fange panikken i rummet. Alder og køn er underordnet, men du skal kunne bevæge dig hurtigt og forstå en planlagt koreografi.

HUSK: At dette er en silent movie drevet af et klassisk soundtrack så derfor er det ekstra vigtigt at man kan arbejde med udtryk om mimik!

Det skal lige understreges at for at komme i betragtning til nogle af rollerne så SKAL ansøgningen sendes via email. Husk at skriv hvilken rolle i kunne være interesseret i og husk at sende opdaterede billeder for at kunne komme i betragtning. Ønsker man at medvirke som statist så husk at skriv om man det er gruppe 1,2 eller 3 man ønsker at medvirke i. Vi caster helt frem til 1.april og der vil også komme et et opslag på DASK hvor i kan ansøge. Vi svarer kun på dem vi ønsker at bruge til projektet. Så hvis det evt er noget for dig så smid en email til:

brook_lynmarvin@hotmail.com

Deadline for ansøgning er 1/4.2026

Præcis dato for optagelser er ikke fastlagt endnu, men holder alle vores udvalgte skuespillere og statister opdateret om forløbet og projektet efterhånden som det skrider frem. 

Projektet laves mht til at det skal vises på diverse film festivaler. Så hvis man går og brænder for at prøve at lave noget anderledes så er det her måske projektet for dig.

Kort synopsis: En respekteret Mafia boss har mistet sit et og alt, nemlig hans datter. Historien starter på en kirkegård hvor vi overværer hendes begravelse, med en hysterisk grædende mor, en masse sørgende håndlangere og mange kondolerende gæster. Iblandt håndlangerne står vores hoved karakter. Da vi zoomer tættere på ham ser vi ham smide en lille tåre, det der skiller ham ud er dog at det er mere en bare sorg vi kan se i ham, han er lige så knust som familien da han var datterens hemmelige elsker. Da vi zoomer mere ind på ham breaker vi over i hans tanker i form af en montage. Hvor vi ser ham eliminere og afhøre flere kriminelle i jagten på hans kærestes morder. Alt dette vil lede op til begravelsen. Der vil komme små brud imellem hans voldelige handlinger hvor han slår over til de små gode kærligheds stunder han havde med hende.

Der skildres imellem en tone af film som The Godfather og Drive. 

Da det hele basically er en silent movie så har vi også valgt at tage os ekstra god tid til at finde de helt rigtige skuespillere til projektet da der her udelukkende skal arbejdes med udtryk og mimik. 
Musikken som vil drive filmen vil være et mix af "Nisi Dominus" af Vivaldi samt nogle andre klassiske stykker. Det hele skydes rundt omkring i Midtjylland men laves til at ligne et mørkt amerikansk drama. 

Dette er et komplet passion projekt så det hele er ulønnet. Men der vil være forplejning og god stemning på alle set.

Action scener vil være koreograferet og vi arbejder efter et koncept hvor vi prøver at få så meget som muligt ud af så lidt som muligt mht til vinkler close ups and so on. 

Vi begynder først at kigge efter skuespillere når det rigtige crew er fundet. Men skulle man falde over det her og tænke at det er lige noget for mig så er man mere end velkommen til at skrive til os. 
Men i første omgang ledes der efter en kameramand der selv har det nødvendige udstyr og som kan se vores vision. Gerne med henblik på et fremtidigt samarbejde til flere produktioner i fremtiden. Så hvis det evt er dig så smid en email til:

brook_lynmarvin@hotmail.com

Deadline for ansøgning er 1/3.2026

Projektet laves mht til at det skal vises på diverse film festivaler. Så hvis man går og brænder for optagelse og editing og har lyst til at prøve at lave noget anderledes så er det her måske projektet for dig.

items.text:
KIARA’S PSALM

**** Filming in Charlotte, NC area in 2026'****

CASTING CALL OF VARIOUS DEMOGRAPHICS 

ALL roles 📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, contact info and reels(if reels are available) to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com 

**Casting now. Don't delay** 

Feature Film | Drama / Music / Thriller

Produced by K-Latt Studios

🎤 CASTING: KIARA LANGSTON (LEAD)

Female | Early to late 20s| African American

A once-rising singer silenced by trauma. A voice the world never forgot.

We are seeking a powerful actress with exceptional singing ability to portray Kiara—a woman reclaiming her voice after tragedy.

✨ Strong vocalist required

✨ Emotional depth & screen presence essential

✨ Star power encouraged

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, reel & singing clips to

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Kiara

🛡️ CASTING: ELIAS CARTER (MALE LEAD)

Male | Early 30s–Late 40s | Open Ethnicity

A highly trained bodyguard. Calm. Protective. Unshakeable.

Elias is strength wrapped in restraint—and the unexpected safe place for a wounded soul.

✨ Strong physically attractive dramatic actor

✨ Subtle, grounded romantic chemistry required

✨ Physically believable, emotionally controlled

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Elias

💛 CASTING: JANESSA REED

Female | 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity 

Best friend. Protector. Truth-teller.

Janessa is the emotional backbone of Kiara’s world—fierce, loving, and unwavering.

✨ Natural charisma

✨ Strong dialogue delivery

✨ Emotionally intelligent performance

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Janessa

🎧 CASTING: DEREK MORRIS

Male | 30s–40s | Open Ethnicity

A trusted member of Kiara’s inner circle.

Derek handles business, security, and hard truths when emotions run high.

✨ Professional presence

✨ Strong supporting performance

✨ Grounded realism

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Derek

🏔️ CASTING: MOTHER CARTER

Female | 60s to 70s | Open Ethnicity

Warm. Watchful. Protective.

The quiet heart of a secluded mountain home offering refuge—and concern.

✨ Subtle, expressive acting

✨ Strong presence with minimal dialogue

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Mother Carter

🪵 CASTING: FATHER CARTER

Male | 60s–70s | Open Ethnicity

A man of principle and restraint.

Protective of his home, wary of danger, loyal to his son.

✨ Controlled, grounded performance

✨ Emotional depth through silence

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Father Carter

🕶️ CASTING: THE OBSESSED FAN (ANTAGONIST)

Male | Late 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity

Charming. Obsessive. Dangerous.

This role requires psychological realism, not theatrics.

⚠️ Dark, nuanced character

✨ Subtle menace & emotional control

✨ Comfort portraying unsettling behavior

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – The Fan

🎙️ CASTING: JOURNALIST / INTERVIEWER

Male or Female | 30s–50s | Open Ethnicity

Poised. Perceptive. Respectful.

The Journalist is the voice guiding Kiara’s story—conducting the interview that frames the film and gently draws out her past, her pain, and her truth. This character must balance professionalism with empathy, knowing when to press and when to listen.

✨ Strong on-camera presence

✨ Natural conversational delivery

✨ Ability to convey depth through listening and subtle reactions

✨ Broadcast or documentary-style experience a plus

This role anchors key emotional moments and requires restraint, intelligence, and authenticity.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Journalist

🧠 CASTING: THERAPIST

Male or Female | 40s–60s | Open Ethnicity

Calm. Grounded. Steady.

The Therapist is a safe space—someone who helps Kiara confront trauma without judgment or pressure. This character doesn’t rescue or lecture; they listen, guide, and gently challenge. Their presence allows Kiara to begin reclaiming her voice.

✨ Deep emotional intelligence

✨ Strong listening and reaction skills

✨ Subtle, naturalistic performance style

✨ Ability to convey warmth, patience, and trust

This role requires restraint, authenticity, and a deep respect for trauma-informed storytelling.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Therapist

🌿 CASTING: MARILYN

Female | 40s–60s | African American

Warm. Faith-filled. Steady.

Marilyn is a gentle presence in Kiara’s life —functioning as both mom and manager, she is someone who knew her before the fame, before the trauma. Rooted in faith and wisdom, Marilyn represents unconditional love, spiritual grounding, and the reminder of who Kiara was before the world broke her.

She speaks dynamically but with purpose. Her words linger. Some singing ability is needed.

✨ Nurturing yet strong presence

✨ Natural, grounded performance

✨ Ability to convey spiritual depth without preaching

✨ Comfort portraying quiet emotional moments

This role is large in impact.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Marilyn 

These are All PAID roles for this feature film. 

GOOD LUCK! See you on set! 

K-latt Studios

🎤 CASTING: KIARA LANGSTON (LEAD)

Female | Early to late 20s| African American

A once-rising singer silenced by trauma. A voice the world never forgot.

We are seeking a powerful actress with exceptional singing ability to portray Kiara—a woman reclaiming her voice after tragedy.

✨ Strong vocalist required

✨ Emotional depth & screen presence essential

✨ Star power encouraged

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, reel & singing clips to

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Kiara

🛡️ CASTING: ELIAS CARTER (MALE LEAD)

Male | Early 30s–Late 40s | Open Ethnicity

A highly trained bodyguard. Calm. Protective. Unshakeable.

Elias is strength wrapped in restraint—and the unexpected safe place for a wounded soul.

✨ Strong physically attractive dramatic actor

✨ Subtle, grounded romantic chemistry required

✨ Physically believable, emotionally controlled

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Elias

💛 CASTING: JANESSA REED

Female | 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity 

Best friend. Protector. Truth-teller.

Janessa is the emotional backbone of Kiara’s world—fierce, loving, and unwavering.

✨ Natural charisma

✨ Strong dialogue delivery

✨ Emotionally intelligent performance

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Janessa

🎧 CASTING: DEREK MORRIS

Male | 30s–40s | Open Ethnicity

A trusted member of Kiara’s inner circle.

Derek handles business, security, and hard truths when emotions run high.

✨ Professional presence

✨ Strong supporting performance

✨ Grounded realism

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Derek

🏔️ CASTING: MOTHER CARTER

Female | 60s to 70s | Open Ethnicity

Warm. Watchful. Protective.

The quiet heart of a secluded mountain home offering refuge—and concern.

✨ Subtle, expressive acting

✨ Strong presence with minimal dialogue

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Mother Carter

🪵 CASTING: FATHER CARTER

Male | 60s–70s | Open Ethnicity

A man of principle and restraint.

Protective of his home, wary of danger, loyal to his son.

✨ Controlled, grounded performance

✨ Emotional depth through silence

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Father Carter

🕶️ CASTING: THE OBSESSED FAN (ANTAGONIST)

Male | Late 20s–40s | Open Ethnicity

Charming. Obsessive. Dangerous.

This role requires psychological realism, not theatrics.

⚠️ Dark, nuanced character

✨ Subtle menace & emotional control

✨ Comfort portraying unsettling behavior

📩 Submit to Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – The Fan

🎙️ CASTING: JOURNALIST / INTERVIEWER

Male or Female | 30s–50s | Open Ethnicity

Poised. Perceptive. Respectful.

The Journalist is the voice guiding Kiara’s story—conducting the interview that frames the film and gently draws out her past, her pain, and her truth. This character must balance professionalism with empathy, knowing when to press and when to listen.

✨ Strong on-camera presence

✨ Natural conversational delivery

✨ Ability to convey depth through listening and subtle reactions

✨ Broadcast or documentary-style experience a plus

This role anchors key emotional moments and requires restraint, intelligence, and authenticity.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Journalist

🧠 CASTING: THERAPIST

Male or Female | 40s–60s | Open Ethnicity

Calm. Grounded. Steady.

The Therapist is a safe space—someone who helps Kiara confront trauma without judgment or pressure. This character doesn’t rescue or lecture; they listen, guide, and gently challenge. Their presence allows Kiara to begin reclaiming her voice.

✨ Deep emotional intelligence

✨ Strong listening and reaction skills

✨ Subtle, naturalistic performance style

✨ Ability to convey warmth, patience, and trust

This role requires restraint, authenticity, and a deep respect for trauma-informed storytelling.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Therapist

🌿 CASTING: MARILYN

Female | 40s–60s | African American

Warm. Faith-filled. Steady.

Marilyn is a gentle presence in Kiara’s life —functioning as both mom and manager, she is someone who knew her before the fame, before the trauma. Rooted in faith and wisdom, Marilyn represents unconditional love, spiritual grounding, and the reminder of who Kiara was before the world broke her.

She speaks dynamically but with purpose. Her words linger. Some singing ability is needed.

✨ Nurturing yet strong presence

✨ Natural, grounded performance

✨ Ability to convey spiritual depth without preaching

✨ Comfort portraying quiet emotional moments

This role is large in impact.

📩 Submit headshot, full body photo, and acting reel to:

Klattstudioscasting@gmail.com

Subject: Kiara’s Psalm – Marilyn 

These are All PAID roles for this feature film. 

GOOD LUCK! See you on set! 

K-latt Studios

items.text:
Vicky Boone Casting is looking for a real little league Baseball team for background roles in an Academy Sports commercial. 
Details below:

Project: Academy Sports
Production Company: The Bear
Project Type:  Social Media Campaign (will run 2 weeks)
Union Status: Non-Union
Project Rate: $250/day per family member
Shoot Date(s): January 21-23 OR 22-24, 2026 (will shoot 1 day within this range)
Shoot Location: Austin, TX. Must work local to Austin.

—
We are looking for:
[REAL LITTLE LEAGUE BASEBALL TEAM] Boys, Ages 11-12. We’re seeking a racially diverse group with natural enthusiasm and chemistry. Players should all be mid-high level skillset wise. Casting 12 players and 1-2 Coaches.

If you and your team might be a fit and are interested in submitting, please submit ASAP to submissions@vickyboonecasting.com by sending the following info:
*Name
*City you and your team are based in
*Contact Number
*Two recent photos (one of you and one of your team)
*Confirm you are avail for all the dates mentioned or list conflicts (1/21-1/23, 1/22-1/24, 2026)
*Please tell us a little bit about your team!
*Please use the subject line “LITTLE LEAGUE TEAM”

We look forward to your submissions!
Team VBC

sharedPost.text:
Happy Holidays from Selfcast 🎄✨
To all our talents, producers, casters and partners — thank you for an unforgettable 2025. We’re sharing this beautiful new film with Søstrene Grene as a little holiday gift and a huge thank you for the trust, teamwork and artistry this year. 💫

We just lived the dream. ✨
So proud that Selfcast helped bring Søstrene Grene’s first international brand campaign to life — with a powerful cast of ballet dancers who gave the film its heartbeat.

As Choreographer/Caster — Maria Christina Jarltoft, it felt like the best kind of time warp: the craft of commercials from 25 years ago — and a heartbeat back on stage from my ballet years.

Full credits & thanks to:
Agency/Creative: @boyespellerberg @Pobeyboye
Directors: @storm__hansen @michaelhansen_mic @tuewstorm
Production: @nicolai_berthelsen
Casting/Choreography: @Selfcastapp — @mariachristinaselfcast
Stylist: @hlindvig

Our incredible ballet cast: @emmajarltoft @valdemarwalter @sara.diona @nahiagilharris @josephine2605 @ameliaidabang

Post/VFX: @hitchvfx @chemistry_film @larsenvfx
Rasmus Skjøtt, René Tingskov, Lotte Korntved, Jacob Holst Mouritzen, Dennis Lee
… and a long list of dedicated people across 17+ markets.

Thank you all — and Merry Christmas & Happy New Year!
Please tag anyone I missed below so we can add everyone who made this happen. 🙏

#Selfcast #CastingMadeEasy #Ballet #Choreography #InternationalCampaign #SøstreneGrene #Production #Creativity #BrandFilm #HappyHolidays #MerryChristmas
